name: html-parser-react
description: the parser for html string transform to react dom

scripts.initial: cd example && npm i && npm start
scripts.release: npm version patch && cd package && npm version patch && npm publish
scripts.version:s: npm version prepatch -m '[prepatch]' && cd package && npm version prepatch -m '[prepatch]'
scripts.version:m: npm version preminor -m '[preminor]' && cd package && npm version preminor -m '[preminor]'
scripts.version:b: npm version premajor -m '[premajor]' && cd package && npm version premajor -m '[premajor]'

author: amschan
